high_descs: Go to the sofa ahead and slightly to the left.
Pick up the knife from the sofa on the seat jutting out from the side.
Look down at the potato on the same seat of the sofa.
Slice the potato with the knife.
Turn around and head straight past the dining table into the kitchen area, approaching the sink.
Place the knife on the plate on the counters to the left of the sink.
Return to the sofa where you sliced the potato.
Pick up one slice of the potato.
Go back to the kitchen area, going to the microwave opposite the sink.
Use the microwave on the potato slice.
Turn around and go back to the counters next to the sink.
Place the potato slice on the counter next to the plate and knife.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, microwave one slice of it and place that slice on a kitchen counter.

high_descs: TURN AROUND TO REACH THE SOFA
TAKE KNIFE FROM SOFA
TURN LEFT TO REACH POTATO
CUT POTATO INTO PIECES
TURN 3 RIGHTS TO REACH THE SINK
KEEP THE KNIFE NEAR THE SINK
TURN AROUND AND LEFT TO REach the sofa
take one piece of potato from sofa
take 3 rights to reach microwave oven
keep the potato inside oven and take out after sometime
turn around to reach the sink
keep the potato in the sink
Turn left and go to the sofa.
Pick up the knife on the sofa.
Turn to the potato on the sofa.
Slice the potato on the sofa.
Turn right toward the table then turn right and go across to the counter top beside the sink.
Place the knife in the plate on the counter top beside the sink.
Turn left go toward the fridge, then turn left and go to the sofa.
Pick up a slice of the potato from the middle.
Turn around and go to the fridge and turn right, then turn around to the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave, heat the potato, then pick the potato back up.
Turn around to the counter top beside the sink.
Place the potato on the counter top beside the sink in the left front corner closer to the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of potato on the counter top beside the sink.
